# ============================================================================
# Git Ignore File
# ============================================================================
# This file tells Git which files and folders to ignore (not track)
# These files should not be committed to version control
#
# Why ignore files?
# - Sensitive data (API keys, passwords)
# - Generated files (build outputs)
# - Dependencies (can be reinstalled)
# - System files (OS-specific)
# - Large files (models, datasets)
# ============================================================================

